{"tid":611504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔平衡嘅關係","createTime":"2018-03-31T05:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T06:13:32.000Z","uid":158220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7bc91866c8e6db7592a192292f71b480c420d0","tid":611504,"uid":158220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"有無人都係一段咁嘅關係入面？<br />\n<br />\n佢出得去玩我唔得<br />\n佢要求check電話但我唔check得佢<br />\n佢唔會認錯，就算係佢錯都係我錯<br />\n小事就發好大脾氣，佢自己做過類似但仲衰嘅就expect人好快開心返<br />\n<br />\n好多次都係我好委屈咁認錯，為左維持段關係<br />\n拍拖拍到好多唔開心屈係心入面，仲要扮唔記仇<br />\n<br />\n仲要成日玩分手，我每次都當真，好辛苦先氹返佢<br />\n佢一d都唔會體諒<br />\n<br />\n點樣先可以令關係平衡d？定係一切已成定局？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b049b654923c0dcb8b402ac7dd699395e3eda9","tid":611504,"uid":154986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"仲慘過做女兵喎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cca6dd98f3420c038df497f77a71756c99436a","tid":611504,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"32453be0afdba5b8e9c3acba9276de7201b85723","tid":611504,"uid":41960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"一定唔止你一條仔"},{"pid":"ec27cc037a6611712d6367feccfec02165be2d5a","tid":611504,"uid":158220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32453be0afdba5b8e9c3acba9276de7201b85723","tid":611504,"uid":41960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"一定唔止你一條仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42447a25c6507d32e4bed493dea98df8594f6767","tid":611504,"uid":41960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec27cc037a6611712d6367feccfec02165be2d5a","tid":611504,"uid":158220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32453be0afdba5b8e9c3acba9276de7201b85723","tid":61150